      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically new but without that brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
