    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp via six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut with a factory-spec subframe and refreshed bushings, while the variable M Differential Lock ensures optimal power delivery. Recent comprehensive preventative maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates within exacting tolerances. Finished in a flawless coat of Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this is a mechanically sorted, collector-tier specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
